{"TopicId":57306,"ForumId":39,"TopicTitle":"Larry Kerman: Kerbaboy!","CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-12-22T13:02:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-12-22T13:02:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIf the show I\u0027m making a tribute to wasn\u0027t part of your childhood, that\u0027s a pity, but you may enjoy this silliness anyway.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt was one of those things where you have an idea, then think \u0022I\u0027m definitelly doing that in KSP later.\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003ELarry Kerman: \u0022Kerbiburg needs a hero!\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003E\u0022I. Am. That. Hero!\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/25d34YN\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/25d34YN.png\u0022 alt=\u002225d34YN.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003E\u0022They call me...\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003E\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003EKerbaboy!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003E\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/L3bNK7T\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/L3bNK7T.png\u0022 alt=\u0022L3bNK7T.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003EBob Kerman: \u0022Oh Hey Larry.\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003ELarry: \u0022Hello there citizen! My name is \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003EKerbaboy.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/c8tjLub\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/c8tjLub.png\u0022 alt=\u0022c8tjLub.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBob: \u0022Right. Why have you stuck communitrons to the side of your space helmet?\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELarry: \u0022Oh, you must be referring to my Super Suction Ears.\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBob: \u0022Super suction ears?\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELarry: \u0022It\u0027s my superpower! Let me demonstrate.\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/y9vEoRo\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/y9vEoRo.png\u0022 alt=\u0022y9vEoRo.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELarry: \u0022 Ah... they seem to be malfunctioning.. I\u0027m a little stuck.. Um... Citizen? Bob! A little help over here?\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-12-22T14:37:48Z\u0022 title=\u002212/22/2013 02:37  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 22, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Tw1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sesni","CreatedById":50625,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-12-22T13:11:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHeh! I like the communitrons in his helmet. Images aren\u0027t loading correctly for my phone though. Vacation did not include internet\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-12-22T13:11:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/xWy5hmo\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/xWy5hmo.png\u0022 alt=\u0022xWy5hmo.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003EAlfred: \u0022I have been making modifications to the Kerbamobile. They haven\u0027t been tested yet, but I think you\u0027ll find them very useful.\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003ELarry: \u0022Oh. That explains all these new buttons.\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003EAlfred: \u0022Try pressing the orange button.\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/MYAcpvk\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/MYAcpvk.png\u0022 alt=\u0022MYAcpvk.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003EAlfred: \u0022Sorry, I meant the yellow button.\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003ELarry: \u0022Oh wow! Wings!\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/1NWfCuH\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/1NWfCuH.png\u0022 alt=\u00221NWfCuH.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/6clvjyK\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/6clvjyK.png\u0022 alt=\u00226clvjyK.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/HkRiEFC\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/HkRiEFC.png\u0022 alt=\u0022HkRiEFC.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003ETrue to the original, this vehicle flings away its wheels dramatically during its \u0022conversion\u0022 to flying mode. Why the one in the TV show did this never made sense to me. \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-12-22T14:35:14Z\u0022 title=\u002212/22/2013 02:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 22, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Tw1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-12-22T14:14:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Sesni\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Sesni\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHeh! I like the communitrons in his helmet. Images aren\u0027t loading correctly for my phone though. Vacation did not include internet\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPity about lack of internet. I think it would\u0027ve been better with the old, smaller dishes, but these are fine. I tried to use KAS grappling hooks first, but they wouldn\u0027t go on the right way. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOne more set of pictures:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/zvs1Jzz\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/zvs1Jzz.png\u0022 alt=\u0022zvs1Jzz.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003EAlfred: \u0022Now, press the green button.\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/t49JqJS\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/t49JqJS.png\u0022 alt=\u0022t49JqJS.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003ELarry: \u0022My wings! I need those!\u0022 \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial;\u0022\u003EAlfred: \u0022No you don\u0027t, not where you\u0027re going!\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003ETunneling mode!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/6lCVO14\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/6lCVO14.png\u0022 alt=\u00226lCVO14.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlso, here are some images of \u0022Kerbaboy\u0022 and Bob, hanging around the Kerbamobile, (Which somehow regained its wheels) posing near KSC.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/AiMGTai\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/AiMGTai.png\u0022 alt=\u0022AiMGTai.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt has a K for Kerbaboy on it. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/YqcKqBz\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/YqcKqBz.png\u0022 alt=\u0022YqcKqBz.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/jXJRF21\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/jXJRF21.png\u0022 alt=\u0022jXJRF21.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-12-22T14:32:42Z\u0022 title=\u002212/22/2013 02:32  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 22, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Tw1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-12-22T17:21:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFunny \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWe need more adventures of Kerbaboy!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dart_Tech","CreatedById":96939,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-12-22T17:26:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOMG I LOVE THIS!!! Priceless! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Jedi Master","CreatedById":57348,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-12-22T18:52:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EReminds me of the 1960\u0027s version of Batman. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xacktar","CreatedById":88876,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-12-23T02:04:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDoes he have a theme song yet?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-12-23T03:46:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Jedi Master\u0022 data-cite=\u0022The Jedi Master\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EReminds me of the 1960\u0027s version of Batman. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFigures. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E Kerbaboy is based on Veggietales\u0027 Larryboy, who in turn, was based on that version of batman. So in a way, Kerbaboy is based on Batman by proxy. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022 data-cite=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EFunny \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWe need more adventures of Kerbaboy!\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMaybe, I have some ideas. If I get him out again, I\u0027ll probably try something with KAS winches, so he can fire the super suction ears out at things. And perhaps with a little photoshoping, a very well known celestial body could be used to make a very kerbal version of \u0022The Fib (powered monster) From Outer Space.\u0022 \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xacktar\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Xacktar\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EDoes he have a theme song yet?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENot yet, I though about recruiting some back up singers, and shooting some scenes based on his vegitable-based inspirer\u0027s music video, but it doesn\u0027t quite have the feel of a theme song to me.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Jedi Master","CreatedById":57348,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-12-23T16:39:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tw1\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Tw1\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EFigures. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E Kerbaboy is based on Veggietales\u0027 Larryboy, who in turn, was based on that version of batman. So in a way, Kerbaboy is based on Batman by proxy.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMan, I remember that show! Big part of my childhood! Yeah, it was a bit preachy, but it was really part of the charm. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-12-26T02:44:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDid a test photoshop of \u0022the fib from space\u0022 and it looked pretty terrible. So I think I\u0027ll stick to other things, as that didn\u0027t seem much fun. But Kerbaboy might do a few more random stunts.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ll be adventuriing in an amphibious explorer on Eve before too long, and I\u0027ve had an idea for a space program origin story that\u0027s been floating around in my head for a while now. Hope no one steals my core idea before I get to it.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-12-26T02:47:37Z\u0022 title=\u002212/26/2013 02:47  AM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 26, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Tw1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}